fields.Title: SEAFORT INT / BLAST DOOR
fields.Description: blast door interactable dialogue. (this is closed, no way to open, open from console if has fuel in)

fields.Title: Cuno: ""What do you think that shit's for?..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "What do you think that shit's for? Let's press some buttons." He points to the console at the other end of the room.

fields.Title: You: "What's on the other side?"
fields.Dialogue Text: What's on the other side?

fields.Title: You: ""You're right. We open the big one..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You're right. We open the big one -- do you see controls somewhere?"

fields.Title: Small Blast Door: "The heavy metal door stands as it d..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The heavy metal door stands as it did, firmly rusted shut into its big brother.

fields.Title: Small Blast Door: "Fuel --> generator --> console. See..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Fuel --> generator --> console. Seems like an obvious path, now that the power is on.

fields.Title: Interfacing: "He's right. It would be better to o..."
fields.Dialogue Text: He's right. It would be better to open its *big brother*. A powerful engine hangs beneath the ceiling -- it must control the blast door.

fields.Title: You: "[Leave.]"
fields.Dialogue Text: [Leave.]

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Maybe this is one of the doors we..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Maybe this is one of the doors we *don't* open?" He looks at the door, then at its bigger brother, then at the lockâ€¦

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""All right." The lieutenant knocks..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "All right." The lieutenant knocks on the metal. "I retract my statement. It was naive. Let's look around and get it open."

fields.Title: Interfacing: "He's right. It would be better to o..."
fields.Dialogue Text: He's right. It would be better to open its *big brother*. A powerful engine hangs under the ceiling -- it must control the blast door.

fields.Title: You: ""No, this isn't 'One More Door'. We..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "No, this isn't 'One More Door'. We're opening it."

fields.Title: Small Blast Door: "Fuel --> generator --> console. See..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Fuel --> generator --> console. Seems like the obvious path.

fields.Title: You: ""I find that highly unlikely.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "I find that highly unlikely."

fields.Title: You: ""One of the *very few doors*? Perha..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "One of the *very few doors*? Perhaps..."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Fuckin' A, let's get this shit ope..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Fuckin' A, let's get this shit open. Get to the secrets behind. Secret style." He stares at the large doors looming above him.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Fuel -- generator -- console. That..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Fuel -- generator -- console. That's our best chance." He points to the console at the other end of the room. "That there could open it, now that the power's on."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Yeah, the console over there?" He..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yeah, the console over there?" He points to the southeast. "Yeah. Yeah. Let's get this big shit open."
fields.Alternate1: "Yeah, the console over there. Remember?" He points to the southeast. "Buttons and shit. Yeah. Yeah. Let's get this big shit open, seems like the best plan."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Another part of the island probabl..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Another part of the island probably." The lieutenant looks into the keyhole. "The lock looks like it could still be usable."

fields.Title: Interfacing: "Perhaps you could open its *big bro..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Perhaps you could open its *big brother*? A powerful engine hangs beneath the ceiling -- it must control the blast door. There must be controls somewhere...

fields.Title: Cuno: ""We fuelled the generator, didn't w..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "We fuelled the generator, didn't we?" He points to the console at the other end of the room. "What do you think that shit's for? Let's press some buttons."

fields.Title: You: ""Sure, you're right. We won't have..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Sure, you're right. We won't have to open it."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""I think there's a console just sou..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I think there's a console just southeast..."  He shuffles his feet to stay warm. "Let's look around. Getting the blast door open seems like the best plan."
fields.Alternate1: "Yeah -- on the console just southeast of here. Remember?" He points to it, then shuffles his feet to stay warm. "Let's look around. Getting the blast door open seems like the best plan."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Fuel -- generator -- console. That..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Fuel -- generator -- console. That's our best chance." He points to the console at the other end of the room. "That there could open it, once we've put some fuel in the generator."

fields.Title: Small Blast Door: "How indeed? Finding the key seems u..."
fields.Dialogue Text: How indeed? Finding the key seems unlikely...

fields.Title: You: ""No. This is the titular *One More..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "No. This is the titular *One More Door*. We're opening it."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: "The lieutenant knocks on the metal...."
fields.Dialogue Text: The lieutenant knocks on the metal. "I retract my statement. It was naive. Let's look around and get it open."

fields.Title: You: ""You're right. We open the big one..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "You're right. We open the big one -- do you see controls anywhere?"

fields.Title: You: ""Sure, you're right. We won't have..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Sure, you're right. We won't have to open it."

fields.Title: You: ""I find us not opening it highly un..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I find us not opening it highly unlikely."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Cuno don't know how to pick this l..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Cuno don't know how to pick this lock. This one's... military shit." He looks at the door, then at its bigger brother, then at the lock.

fields.Title: Logic: "The chances of there being 'importa..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The chances of there being 'important shit' there are rather high, yes.

fields.Title: You: "How do I open this?"
fields.Dialogue Text: How do I open this?

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Another part of Death Island? Some..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Another part of Death Island? Some secret hidden shit, Cuno thinks. Important shit..."

fields.Title: Small Blast Door: "The door is mute, cold as ice. The..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The door is mute, cold as ice. The lock looks like it may have seen recent use, but it's impossible to tell.

fields.Title: Small Blast Door: "You see a small metal door nested i..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You see a small metal door nested inside a larger one -- a heavy steel blast door. There is a conventional keyhole above the handle. It's very small.
